{"body":[{"content":"「字幕由 富睿字幕组 搬运」\n（禁止在B站宣传漫游相关内容，否则拉黑）","location":2,"from":0,"to":0.65},{"content":"「字幕由 富睿字幕组 搬运」\n（禁止在B站宣传漫游相关内容，否则拉黑）\n创造神始祖","from":0.65,"location":2,"to":2.53},{"content":"被自己创造出的所谓的恶神们毁灭了","from":2.53,"location":2,"to":6.99},{"content":"随后诸神纷争的时代便拉开序幕","from":7.2,"location":2,"to":11.08},{"content":"神殿里的巨大雕像","from":11.08,"location":2,"to":13.08},{"content":"都是善良的神明对吗","from":13.08,"location":2,"to":15.08},{"content":"对人类而言 确实如此","from":15.08,"location":2,"to":18.0},{"content":"什么意思","from":18.09,"location":2,"to":19.71},{"content":"在众口相传的传说中","from":20.05,"location":2,"to":22.05},{"content":"诸神之王","from":22.05,"location":2,"to":23.55},{"content":"掌管秩序和裁决的雷神沃尔特","from":23.55,"location":2,"to":26.55},{"content":"曾与他的哥哥 战神伊鲁特雷特有过一战","from":26.55,"location":2,"to":30.22},{"content":"伊鲁特雷特首战告捷","from":30.31,"location":2,"to":32.93},{"content":"但沃尔特在妻子地母神玛可尔的加护下","from":32.93,"location":2,"to":36.65},{"content":"将战神驱逐到地底","from":36.65,"location":2,"to":39.52},{"content":"战神沉入地底","from":39.86,"location":2,"to":42.15},{"content":"虎视眈眈地企图复仇","from":42.15,"location":2,"to":44.82},{"content":"类似的传说有很多 但大致情形都是如此","from":45.11,"location":2,"to":49.16},{"content":"你怎么看呢","from":49.16,"location":2,"to":50.58},{"content":"那只是寓言而已吧","from":51.16,"location":2,"to":53.33},{"content":"哦","from":53.33,"location":2,"to":54.37},{"content":"世间的统治虽然始于暴力专制","from":54.96,"location":2,"to":58.75},{"content":"但随着农耕的发展","from":58.75,"location":2,"to":60.71},{"content":"于是秩序和法律主导的社会就出现了","from":60.71,"location":2,"to":62.71},{"content":"不过随着时间推移","from":62.71,"location":2,"to":64.72},{"content":"暴力还将卷土重来","from":64.72,"location":2,"to":66.72},{"content":"这种吧","from":66.72,"location":2,"to":67.8},{"content":"你果然很敏锐啊","from":67.8,"location":2,"to":70.68},{"content":"掌管秩序和裁决的沃尔特是善神","from":71.39,"location":2,"to":75.31},{"content":"与之相对战神就被看作恶神","from":75.31,"location":2,"to":78.02},{"content":"但假如秩序腐败","from":78.11,"location":2,"to":80.11},{"content":"沃尔特就可以被叫做恶神","from":80.11,"location":2,"to":82.03},{"content":"而打击腐败的伊鲁特雷特","from":82.03,"location":2,"to":84.03},{"content":"也可以被叫做善神","from":84.03,"location":2,"to":86.03},{"content":"也就是说","from":86.53,"location":2,"to":87.57},{"content":"善神与恶神的概念","from":87.57,"location":2,"to":89.49},{"content":"只不过是信仰者给安的名号罢了","from":89.49,"location":2,"to":93.7},{"content":"说了这番话","from":93.7,"location":2,"to":95.16},{"content":"神官们大概会不高兴吧","from":95.16,"location":2,"to":98.0},{"content":"当然你可别对玛丽说哦","from":98.0,"location":2,"to":100.5},{"content":"不会说的","from":100.79,"location":2,"to":102.05},{"content":"说到底","from":102.05,"location":2,"to":102.88},{"content":"神明考虑事物的方式跟我们完全不在一个维度","from":102.88,"location":2,"to":107.05},{"content":"人类衡量善恶的标准是无法衡量他们的想法的","from":107.59,"location":2,"to":112.35},{"content":"怎么说呢","from":112.64,"location":2,"to":114.52},{"content":"伽斯你好酷啊","from":114.52,"location":2,"to":115.39},{"content":"“酷”是什么意思","from":115.73,"location":2,"to":116.81},{"content":"呃 就是一种打破常规的感觉","from":116.81,"location":2,"to":120.31},{"content":"虽然小孩子就是时不时喜欢瞎造一些词语","from":120.69,"location":2,"to":124.03},{"content":"不过这个词的发音听上去还不赖","from":124.03,"location":2,"to":126.24},{"content":"照亮前行之路的光","from":126.96,"location":2,"to":131.78},{"content":"在此醒来 本以为是对自己的惩罚","from":137.34,"location":2,"to":143.96},{"content":"那天看到的景色却改变了一切","from":143.96,"location":2,"to":149.98},{"content":"即使看不见未来 被黑暗所吞噬","from":150.78,"location":2,"to":157.58},{"content":"那时候赋予我的东西就在于此","from":157.58,"location":2,"to":164.78},{"content":"仅仅依靠语言是危险的","from":164.9,"location":2,"to":168.24},{"content":"不能光靠力量","from":168.24,"location":2,"to":171.66},{"content":"如果能正视自己站起来","from":171.66,"location":2,"to":175.08},{"content":"就能去战斗","from":175.08,"location":2,"to":178.54},{"content":"渴望生存 祈祷","from":179.16,"location":2,"to":182.88},{"content":"因为曾发誓会去实现","from":182.88,"location":2,"to":185.96},{"content":"所以坚强面对 即使是绝望之路","from":185.96,"location":2,"to":190.28},{"content":"也会继续前行","from":190.28,"location":2,"to":192.7},{"content":"想要守护 重要的东西","from":192.7,"location":2,"to":196.62},{"content":"振作起来","from":196.62,"location":2,"to":199.7},{"content":"不移开视线 不畏惧","from":199.7,"location":2,"to":203.36},{"content":"坚定决心 举起神圣的灯火","from":203.36,"location":2,"to":211.64},{"content":"想要进入无我的境界","from":220.5,"location":2,"to":222.37},{"content":"并不是说要什么都不想","from":222.5,"location":2,"to":224.38},{"content":"而是将过去和未来都逐出脑海","from":225.09,"location":2,"to":227.0},{"content":"全神贯注于“此刻”","from":227.21,"location":2,"to":229.13},{"content":"将此时此刻渺小的自己","from":230.51,"location":2,"to":232.84},{"content":"展现在神明面前","from":232.84,"location":2,"to":234.59},{"content":"然后","from":235.3,"location":2,"to":236.26},{"content":"不断潜入","from":236.26,"location":2,"to":237.81},{"content":"没有尽头","from":238.1,"location":2,"to":239.06},{"content":"五天的“沉默祈祷”修行结束了","from":247.65,"location":2,"to":251.61},{"content":"辛苦了","from":251.78,"location":2,"to":252.95},{"content":"这五天里","from":254.2,"location":2,"to":255.45},{"content":"我不断地在祈祷","from":255.45,"location":2,"to":257.45},{"content":"身体没有不舒服吧 威尔","from":258.62,"location":2,"to":261.08},{"content":"嗯 没事","from":261.16,"location":2,"to":262.46},{"content":"你明明才13岁 真是了不起","from":262.62,"location":2,"to":265.42},{"content":"因为一直都在和玛丽一起祈祷啊","from":265.54,"location":2,"to":268.34},{"content":"双手受伤之后已经过了五年","from":271.88,"location":2,"to":275.18},{"content":"尽管靠玛丽的祈祷术","from":275.59,"location":2,"to":277.05},{"content":"似乎能治愈这些疤痕","from":277.05,"location":2,"to":279.01},{"content":"但我选择保持这样","from":279.22,"location":2,"to":281.02},{"content":"因为布拉多说过这是男人的勋章","from":281.22,"location":2,"to":284.19},{"content":"今天就都做你爱吃的菜吧","from":284.48,"location":2,"to":287.69},{"content":"好耶","from":287.77,"location":2,"to":288.73},{"content":"明天之前全背下来","from":290.23,"location":2,"to":292.65},{"content":"欸","from":292.65,"location":2,"to":293.74},{"content":"伽斯教的内容越来越深奥","from":294.28,"location":2,"to":296.91},{"content":"量也大到可怕","from":296.91,"location":2,"to":298.62},{"content":"但我不认输","from":299.03,"location":2,"to":300.29},{"content":"拼命跟上了进度","from":300.29,"location":2,"to":302.25},{"content":"于是课程变得更加密集了","from":303.16,"location":2,"to":305.96},{"content":"仿佛是在期待我什么时候服输","from":306.54,"location":2,"to":310.09},{"content":"即使如此","from":311.21,"location":2,"to":312.21},{"content":"玛丽和伽斯的修行还算是轻松的","from":312.21,"location":2,"to":314.67},{"content":"好","from":315.72,"location":2,"to":317.05},{"content":"那么就进入今天的正题吧","from":317.64,"location":2,"to":319.43},{"content":"那是什么","from":320.76,"location":2,"to":322.06},{"content":"这是你的对手","from":322.35,"location":2,"to":324.06},{"content":"我在废墟里抓到的","from":324.06,"location":2,"to":325.14},{"content":"不 我不是问这个","from":325.35,"location":2,"to":327.27},{"content":"没事的","from":327.31,"location":2,"to":328.44},{"content":"不过是下等恶魔的尸骨而已","from":328.44,"location":2,"to":330.86},{"content":"恶魔也会变成不死者的吗","from":330.94,"location":2,"to":333.03},{"content":"那就开始吧","from":333.23,"location":2,"to":334.15},{"content":"等…","from":334.15,"location":2,"to":334.82},{"content":"打中了","from":342.87,"location":2,"to":343.75},{"content":"布拉多 我赢了","from":345.83,"location":2,"to":347.58},{"content":"哦 哦 真棒","from":347.58,"location":2,"to":349.83},{"content":"受过训练的战士","from":350.25,"location":2,"to":351.67},{"content":"能凭借训练出来的反射神经去杀死对手","from":351.67,"location":2,"to":353.46},{"content":"就是这个意思啊","from":353.46,"location":2,"to":354.88},{"content":"也 也没错吧","from":354.88,"location":2,"to":356.72},{"content":"布拉多","from":357.3,"location":2,"to":358.43},{"content":"啊 第一次的实战还过得去","from":358.59,"location":2,"to":362.39},{"content":"听好了","from":362.39,"location":2,"to":363.06},{"content":"我只是说还过得去","from":363.06,"location":2,"to":364.47},{"content":"你别得意忘形了","from":364.72,"location":2,"to":365.89},{"content":"啊 原来你在想这个","from":366.06,"location":2,"to":367.52},{"content":"嘿嘿","from":367.6,"location":2,"to":368.56},{"content":"怎么样 我其实是天才吧","from":368.65,"location":2,"to":370.81},{"content":"你说不定就是个天才啊","from":371.11,"location":2,"to":373.32},{"content":"别这样啊 你吐槽吐槽我啊","from":373.32,"location":2,"to":375.57},{"content":"好 那就提前试试更加严苛的吧 天才","from":375.57,"location":2,"to":380.07},{"content":"啊","from":380.16,"location":2,"to":380.62},{"content":"以前总是在山丘上俯瞰的这座废城","from":383.41,"location":2,"to":386.79},{"content":"那一天 我第一次踏入其中","from":387.0,"location":2,"to":389.87},{"content":"地下还有这样的通道啊","from":399.01,"location":2,"to":401.26},{"content":"以前这里住着人类和矮人族","from":401.47,"location":2,"to":404.47},{"content":"打造兵器呀什么的 我也受过他们不少照顾","from":404.47,"location":2,"to":406.47},{"content":"不过如今 这里变成了不会思考的不死者们徘徊的危险地带","from":407.31,"location":2,"to":412.56},{"content":"这就是一直禁止你来这里的原因","from":412.73,"location":2,"to":415.61},{"content":"就这里吧","from":417.11,"location":2,"to":418.07},{"content":"你确认好自己带的东西了吗","from":418.99,"location":2,"to":420.7},{"content":"嗯 剑和盾","from":420.7,"location":2,"to":422.91},{"content":"面包和干肉 还有水袋","from":422.91,"location":2,"to":424.91},{"content":"那就是现在你身上带着的全部物品","from":424.91,"location":2,"to":426.91},{"content":"好 你一个人想办法从这里出去吧","from":427.54,"location":2,"to":429.25},{"content":"欸","from":429.25,"location":2,"to":429.83},{"content":"我在外面等你","from":429.83,"location":2,"to":431.62},{"content":"别死了啊","from":431.62,"location":2,"to":432.79},{"content":"等 等下 布拉多","from":432.79,"location":2,"to":434.63},{"content":"这 这不是开玩笑吧","from":435.92,"location":2,"to":437.76},{"content":"“光”","from":438.17,"location":2,"to":438.88},{"content":"布拉多","from":440.72,"location":2,"to":441.55},{"content":"出口在这个方向吧","from":443.26,"location":2,"to":445.22},{"content":"不过刚才布拉多是不是说过","from":446.06,"location":2,"to":449.02},{"content":"这里是","from":449.02,"location":2,"to":451.02},{"content":"我就知道","from":454.77,"location":2,"to":456.11},{"content":"布拉多应该是在测试我的综合实战能力","from":464.32,"location":2,"to":468.79},{"content":"一个人 原来这么寂寞和不安吗","from":470.46,"location":2,"to":473.5},{"content":"我连这个都忘记了","from":476.04,"location":2,"to":478.0},{"content":"明明前世一直都是一个人","from":478.38,"location":2,"to":480.34},{"content":"但自从来到这个世界"